    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3, featuring the iconic S65 4.0-liter naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant delivers peak torque through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a Variable M Differential Lock. The chassis maintains its composure with an aluminum multi-link rear suspension and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable damping rates. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end remain robust. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity remains high, providing a visceral, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
